maintext:
The J Show
Carmen is calling from the neighborhood association. However, the woman tells Carmen to hold, but she here’s her entire conversation with her kid! Carmen doesn’t mean to be rude, but can she put her on mute please?
title: [Listen] Carmen’s 7am Crank Call: Don’t Put Me On Hold
